\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Sitting up high in the evening. See demons crawling out. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 They\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92re looking - }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Torches}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Fight}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Torches snuffed out.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Down!}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Elrahet -}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 We need to move.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Elrahet does not move.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Looking out the window. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93An Amalgamete will gorge tonight.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We cannot leave.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why not?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93One demon is a nuisance. Twenty is a fright. Hundreds mean an Amalgamete swells out of sight.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Spooky.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We must find the beast and kill it.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You want us to wade down into that horde?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We have the Mazyd.\u8221\'94  She looked at Mandri, eyes twinkling.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Bring it.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Mandri stepped forward.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hold on,\u8221\'94 said Ayram. \u8220\'93If we wake up the Mazyd now, then we\u8217\'92re back where we started.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Worse than where we started.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Elrahet bowed.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Of course, the choice is yours, my Lord Ayram. Though I should remind you of our, one Amalgamete can destroy the world.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Fine.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Elrahet took O, then said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And the Riga.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Seb stepped forward. Spins around.}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What is this? What did you do?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I didn\u8217\'92t do anything.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Its throat is crushed.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Is it?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93What did you do Seb.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I didn\u8217\'92t do anything. It was on my back!\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hey, I didn\u8217\'92t see you offerin\u8217\'92 to carry the damn thing. It\u8217\'92s same as always with you. Do nothin an blame Seb for pulling extra weight. Well I\u8217\'92m sorry the Riga is spoilt, but I\u8217\'92ll go find.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Ayram, intimidating. Seb cowering.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s been one thing after the next with you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s not my fault,\u8221\'94 Seb whined. \u8220\'93Look, we can get another one. It was easy enough the first time, right?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Is that how you make this right? You going to retrace your steps back through that demon infested canyon?\u8221\'94}
